      "_type": "TextBlock",
      "text": [
        {
          "_type": "heading",
          "level": 1,
          "content": [
            {
              "_type": "text",
              "text": "Coming Soon: The Ultimate Resource for TCG Collectors"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "_type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "_type": "text",
              "text": "This website is currently under construction — but something exciting is on the way!"
            },
            {
              "_type": "hardBreak"
            },
            {
              "_type": "hardBreak"
            },
            {
              "_type": "text",
              "text": "Collection.cards",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "_type": "bold"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "_type": "text",
              "text": " aims to become the ultimate resource for TCG collectors. Our goal is to showcase trading cards in the most "
            },
            {
              "_type": "text",
              "text": "realistic and detailed way possible",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "_type": "bold"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "_type": "text",
              "text": ", including all "
            },
            {
              "_type": "text",
              "text": "variants, effects, and print details",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "_type": "bold"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "_type": "text",
              "text": ", so collectors can easily identify and match their cards."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "_type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "_type": "text",
              "text": "You'll also be able to "
            },
            {
              "_type": "text",
              "text": "visualize card placement",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "_type": "bold"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "_type": "text",
              "text": " inside different binder layouts — whether you use 4, 9, 12, or 16-pocket binders. Stack cards in sequence, organize them side-by-side, and see how your full collection fits together."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "_type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "_type": "text",
              "text": "Powerful "
            },
            {
              "_type": "text",
              "text": "filtering and search tools",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "_type": "bold"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "_type": "text",
              "text": " will help you find exactly what you’re looking for — by energy type, rarity, variant, effect, illustrator, and more."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "_type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "_type": "text",
              "text": "Best of all, "
            },
            {
              "_type": "text",
              "text": "Collection.cards will be open source",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "_type": "bold"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "_type": "text",
              "text": ", inviting contributors from around the world to help build and expand this project together."
            },
            {
              "_type": "hardBreak"
            },
            {
              "_type": "hardBreak"
            },
            {
              "_type": "text",
              "text": "Stay tuned — more features, previews, and updates are coming soon!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}